### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Envoyer un devis (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-send-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here"
}

### Test 2 - Erreur: quote_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-send-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Test 3 - Erreur: devis déjà envoyé
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-send-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "already-sent-quote-uuid"
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: devis déjà accepté
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-send-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "accepted-quote-uuid"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: accès non autorisé (client)
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes-send-quote
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quote_id": "quote-uuid-here"
}

